@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uvhuse(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((tmp + 0.91 + v1 + 0.05) * wp.abs(v2 + 0.58)) + v0)
    v2 = (wp.sin(v1) - v0)
    v1 = wp.exp(v2)
    v1 = (((v0 + 0.35 * tmp + 0.79) + 0.71) + (v1 - v1))
    v2 = (tmp * ((tmp + 0.09 - v2 + 0.73) - 0.68))
    data[tid] = v0
